{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Q</strong>: What has eight legs and wields command over the entire space-time continuum?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A</strong>: <strong>Spiders.</strong> WHY IS IT ALWAYS SPIDERS?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/Fire_and_Explosions_Cut_2.gif?t=1734539860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to the multiverse. It's full of spiders.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The one good thing about spiders was that once you left Earth, you didn\u2019t have to deal with them very much. Now they\u2019ve invaded the ENTIRE multiverse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But wherever there exist spiders, there exist those destined to face them down: The Exterminators. That's you, by the way. So strap in, take a deep breath and plunge headlong into one of these interdimensional portals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">That's what we pay you for! You are being paid, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/KIWF2_CoopMulti_GIF.gif?t=1734539860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play with friends in four player co-op or go head-to-head in Spider Hunt PvP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But you don\u2019t need to face your fears alone! Collect your three least arachnophobic friends and play through the entire game in a 4-player, online co-op mode. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Friends not pulling their weight? Challenge them to prove themselves in \u201cSpider Hunt\u201d, a Spiders vs. Exterminators PvP mode where you can play as an arachnid for the first time. Throw webs to slow exterminators down, perform daring acts of parkour to escape justice, or simply hide in a vase and watch the chaos unfold while laughing manically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Of course, the Exterminators will have a host of tools and weapons to hunt spiders down, so you better <i>hope</i> nobody has picked up the tracker...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/Burn_+_window_Suprise_cut.gif?t=1734539860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Arm yourself with the latest in sci-fi weaponry</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Utilize the latest advancements in cutting-edge multiverse technology and upgrades to hunt down the arachnids, then exploit their classic Achilles heel: FLAMES \u2014 or lead showers. Or earth-shattering kabooms, remote control vehicles, lasers\u2026 crushing under heavy objects\u2026 honestly, they're pretty weak to most forms of violence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/Swarm_of_Spiders_cut.gif?t=1734539860\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scream like a big baby when a spider is lurking under your laser pistol.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Murder that spider for startling you. You're not a baby, it was the spider's fault.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play the entire story campaign in four-player online co-op, or fight against friends in the PVP Spider Hunt mode across multiple maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the depths of the multiverse from the Wild West to the very origins of spider-kind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit strange new worlds, discover new life and new civilisations... and absolutely obliterate them in the name of spider-murdering justice!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a brand new story told through the eyes of people not fortunate enough to own their own flamethrowers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/Tanks_Smaller.gif?t=1734539860\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357000/extras/KIWF_Discord_QR_-_612x200.png?t=1734539860\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Compound X Gon' Give It To Ya","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/47585ede089545a0cf0362d0ee94cff968729956.jpg"},{"name":"Tinker, Tailor, Exterminator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/6102a84cb51660615a48cbe5d9f7c66adce34f4d.jpg"},{"name":"Big Spender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/cdab7fa6d19d84330b9aa55000a5e15f1d66e61c.jpg"},{"name":"Story Time","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/93d4693a9a75e9715c4bde4611625465e60a0f80.jpg"},{"name":"Prop Hunt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/9671ffce764fb670d58a871321981ed8a84b5dd1.jpg"},{"name":"Toil and Trouble","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/d4e99c2f4cb486a68a987ea5a3695b3acf3569e3.jpg"},{"name":"Back in Business","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/cc2ce1fac2d4ec0ec854f42af9f0482ae0ece938.jpg"},{"name":"Practice Makes Perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/ab0d93df21cbfe9ff6c8603e4614cef36782a28a.jpg"},{"name":"Speedrun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2357000/d41c81526a1